---
title: Souvlaki Inspired Halloumi Flatbreads with Chips and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Go for gold in the kitchen with our Olympic Games inspired menu! Tuck into these
Souvlaki Inspired Halloumi Flatbreads whilst you're watching Paris 2024 for a winning dinnertime. A popular Greek street food choice, the word souvlaki literally means 'meat on skewers'. However, this doesn't just extend to grilled meat - this vegetarian halloumi version combines indulgence, freshness and flavour all on one tasty flatbread.
